    <h2>About Tea</h2>
    <p>Tea is one of the most popular beverages in the world, enjoyed for its flavor and numerous health benefits. It has a rich history dating back thousands of years.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="types">
    <h2>Types of Tea</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Green Tea:</strong> Fresh and lightly processed.</li>
      <li><strong>Black Tea:</strong> Bold and fully oxidized.</li>
      <li><strong>Oolong Tea:</strong> A balance between green and black tea.</li>
      <li><strong>Herbal Tea:</strong> Infusions made from herbs, flowers, and fruits.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section id="benefits">
    <h2>Health Benefits of Tea</h2>
    <p>Tea is rich in antioxidants and may help improve heart health, boost mental focus, and promote relaxation.</p>
